src:
Stopping a wild goose chase
01 Nov 2019, 18:22 by Steve Ringman
Urban geese are a common sight at Seattle’s parks. Full-grown birds can be 30-45 inches tall, bigger than some young children.
Steve Ringman: sringman@seattletimes.com;
